<item>
            <title>[LU-3972] ACL changes share XATTR flag in changelog</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3972</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently when making ACL changes or XATTR changes, changelog only represents them as &apos;XATTR&apos; change types. This is workable, however requires probing of both ACL and XATTR data to determine what changed (assuming you knew what it was before).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose that ACL changes have their own changelog flag to better identify those changes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
